to run script in crontab use this command
crontab -e
then add this line to file
*/1 * * * * /home/mirexcool/Desktop/HomeTasks/LINUx_BASH_HOMETASK/section_C.sh /home/mirexcool/Desktop/HomeTasks/LINUx_BASH_HOMETASK/test /home/mirexcool/Desktop/HomeTasks/LINUx_BASH_HOMETASK/backup

Where first argument is path to script
/home/mirexcool/Desktop/HomeTasks/LINUx_BASH_HOMETASK/section_C.sh

Second and third is source directory and backup directory
/home/mirexcool/Desktop/HomeTasks/LINUx_BASH_HOMETASK/test /home/mirexcool/Desktop/HomeTasks/LINUx_BASH_HOMETASK/backup

To save all changes in directory to file run script 
directory_logging.sh path

where path is a directory for listening


